WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.471 --> 00:00:07.570
Hi, and welcome to our course,
English for Effective Business Speaking.

2
00:00:07.570 --> 00:00:08.980
I'm Sean McMinn.

3
00:00:08.980 --> 00:00:09.700
Delian Kin and

4
