us on our journey through this course.

5
00:00:14.990 --> 00:00:18.070
We have two main goals for you.

6
00:00:18.070 --> 00:00:22.610
One is to introduce to you and
help you improve your business

7
00:00:22.610 --> 00:00:28.180
communication skills, from job interviews
to business meetings to business pitches.

8
00:00:28.180 --> 00:00:34.990
And our second goal is to help you improve
your spoken English, and this includes

9
00:00:34.990 --> 00:00:41.200
