and the way that you deliver a message.

10
00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:43.190
So those are our two main goals.

11
00:00:43.190 --> 00:00:45.570
And we'll be doing this in many ways.

12
00:00:45.570 --> 00:00:48.570
Throughout the course, you'll be
introduced to different things such as

13
00:00:48.570 --> 00:00:52.860
lecture videos where we give you some
sort of input or recommendations.

14
00:00:52.860 --> 00:00:54.780
And this is followed by activities or

15
00:00:54.780 --> 00:00:59.150
