what we're talking about.

16
00:00:59.150 --> 00:01:03.730
We really encourage you to engage
with others in this course.

17
00:01:03.730 --> 00:01:08.710
Sometimes we have found in courses
like this that a good thing to do

18
00:01:08.710 --> 00:01:10.280
is to get on social media.

19
00:01:10.280 --> 00:01:14.800
Use Skype, use Facebook,
use WeChat, meet other people,

20
00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:19.170
contact them, ask them if you want to
practice your spoken English.

21
00:01:19.170 --> 00:01:21.440
And we find that a lot of people do.

22
00:01:21.440 --> 00:01:26.510
So if you have that opportunity, contact
other people in this course, call them up,

23
00:01:26.510 --> 00:01:29.460
